Package: till
Version: 1.0.0-2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 5), coreutils, mount, util-linux, debootstrap, apt
Maintainer: You <0foo.dev>
Description: Tiny chroot manager for per-project Debian envs
 Provides 'till build' to bootstrap a minimal Debian chroot under the project,
 and 'till enter' to chroot into it with the current working directory bind-mounted.
